name: Bluebunny - An Inkbunny Theme by FennecFoxee
description: Bluebunny is a dark, minimalist theme for the Inkbunny website. It is site wide and will change the whites and greens of Inkbunny to dark gray and blue, respectively.
additional_info:
v0.1.1 - Patched some images that weren't showing up properly

v0.1 - First release, may be a little buggy on some pages, and not all elements are skinned yet.
